-- Buffett’s Berkshire Hathaway Discloses National Oilwell Stake
-- B y   N o a h   B u h a y a r
-- 2012-08-14T20:13:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-14/buffett-s-berkshire-hathaway-discloses-national-oilwell-stake.html
Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A)  took a stake
in  National Oilwell Varco Inc. (NOV)  as billionaire Chairman  Warren
Buffett  made more funds available for the portfolios managed by
deputy stock-pickers.  Buffett’s firm held 2.84 million shares of oilfield
equipment-maker on June 30, his Omaha, Nebraska-based company
said today in a filing disclosing U.S. stockholdings at the end
of the second quarter.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in  New York  at 
 nbuhayar@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  